Step 2: Fix Vercel's API URL
Go to Vercel Dashboard -> Project -> Settings -> Environment Variables.
Look at your VITE_API_URL.
Double-check that it is EXACTLY the link Railway gave you, starting with https:// and ending with /api. Example of a perfect one: https://wa-commerce-production-123.up.railway.app/api
If you change either of these, wait 1-2 minutes for Vercel/Railway to restart!

